            "text": "PSBAR (Public Sector Bodies Accessibility Regulations): applies to all EdTech used in publicly-funded schools. WCAG 2.1 AA mandatory. EdTech-specific accessibility challenges: (1) content with images (diagrams, charts, worksheets) — alt text required for all educational images. (2) video content — captions required (auto-captions from YouTube are insufficient — must be reviewed for accuracy). (3) interactive exercises (drag-and-drop, click-to-match) — keyboard-accessible alternatives required. (4) timed assessments — WCAG 2.1 AA: time limits must have a way to extend (important for pupils with additional support needs)."
